Class Item

  • java.lang.Object
    • edu.cpp.cs.cs141.classproject.Item
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Entity, java.io.Serializable

    public class Item
extends java.lang.Object
implements Entity, java.io.Serializable
    The Item class represents an item that the player can pick up. It can be either an invincibility powerup, an extra bullet, or a radar that determines where the briefcase is.
    Author:
    Natanael Ariawan, David Hau, Miguel Menjivar, Aidan Novobilski
    See Also:
